      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This example has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, exhibiting a condition that reflects its original showroom delivery state. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail denotes a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled preservation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unparalleled aesthetic and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
